additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with skin. Do not use as a baby wipe or for personal hygiene. Hard surface disinfectant only. Not to be used on skin. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone: Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 166) or a doctor. If swallowed, do NOT induce vomiting. Give a glass of water to drink. If skin contact occurs wash skin thoroughly. Will irritate eyes. If in eyes, wash out immediately with a large amount of water. Remove contact lenses, if present and easy to do. Continue rinsing. If irritation persists, contact a doctor.
